'''馬奴·賈西亞-魯爾福'''（{{lang-es|Manuel Garcia-Rulfo}}，{{bd|1981年|2月25日}}）是一位[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]男演員<ref>{{cite web|title=Manuel Garcia-Rulfo - IMDb|url=http://www.imdb.com/name/nm2636310/|website=[[Internet_Movie_Database|Internet Movie Database]]|accessdate=2016-08-10|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126002201/https://www.imdb.com/name/nm2636310/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

參演過的著名作品如電影《{{le|希望之眼 (電影)|Bless Me, Ultima (film)|希望之眼}}》（2013年）和《[[蛋糕的滋味|蛋糕的滋味]]》（2014年），以及電視劇《{{le|惡夜追殺令：影集|From Dusk till Dawn: The Series}}》（2014年至2015年）<ref>{{cite news|url=http://varietylatino.com/2014/gente/noticias/manuel-garcia-rulfo-con-jennifer-aniston-cake-adriana-barraza-23373/|title=El mexicano Manuel García Rulfo trabajará junto a Jennifer Aniston en ‘Cake’|author=Flores, Griselda|website=Variety Latino|date=2014-04-15|accessdate=2016-09-23|archive-date=2020-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200216122332/http://varietylatino.com/2014/gente/noticias/manuel-garcia-rulfo-con-jennifer-aniston-cake-adriana-barraza-23373/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而他也在改編自1960年西部動作片《[[豪勇七蛟龍|豪勇七蛟龍]]》的《[[絕地7騎士|絕地7騎士]]》（2016年）中參與演出<ref name="rulfo" />。2022年於[[Netflix|Netflix]]影集《{{le|下流正義 (電視劇)|The Lincoln Lawyer (TV series)|下流正義}}》主演{{le|米奇·哈勒|Mickey Haller}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2021/01/the-lincoln-lawyer-drama-david-e-kelley-netflix-series-order-manuel-garcia-rulfo-star-formerly-at-cbs-1234666034/|title='The Lincoln Lawyer' Drama From David E. Kelley Lands Netflix Series Order; Manuel Garcia-Rulfo To Star|date=2021-01-11|first=Nellie|last=Andreeva|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112020335/https://deadline.com/2021/01/the-lincoln-lawyer-drama-david-e-kelley-netflix-series-order-manuel-garcia-rulfo-star-formerly-at-cbs-1234666034/|archive-date=2021-01-12|url-status=live|access-date=2021-01-12}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2021/tv/news/lincoln-lawyer-tv-series-netflix-1234882601/|title='Lincoln Lawyer' TV Adaptation Moves to Netflix With Series Order, '6 Underground's' Manuel Garcia-Rulfo to Star|date=2021-01-11|first=Joe|last=Otterson|website=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112022122/https://variety.com/2021/tv/news/lincoln-lawyer-tv-series-netflix-1234882601/|archive-date=2021-01-12|url-status=live|access-date=2021-01-12}}</ref>。

== 早期生活 ==
賈西亞-魯爾福出生於[[哈利斯科州|哈利斯科州]][[瓜達拉哈拉_(墨西哥)|瓜達拉哈拉]]，在此學會了騎馬<ref name="rulfo">{{cite news|url=http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/articulo/espectaculos/cine/2016/07/27/manuel-garcia-rulfo-se-vuelve-fugitivo|title=Manuel García Rulfo se vuelve fugitivo|author=Huerta, César|website=El Universal|date=2016-07-27|accessdate=2016-09-23|archive-date=2020-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200426033936/https://www.eluniversal.com.mx/articulo/espectaculos/cine/2016/07/27/manuel-garcia-rulfo-se-vuelve-fugitivo|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他就讀當地的{{le|德爾瓦勒代阿特馬傑大學|Universidad del Valle de Atemajac}}，實現了對電影的熱情。他曾就讀於[[美國|美國]]的[[紐約電影學院|紐約電影學院]]，但決定回墨西哥繼續演藝事業<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.quien.com/sociales/2009/08/04/manuel-garcia-rulfo-galan-de-pelicula|title=Manuel García Rulfo - Galán de Película|author=Domene, Daniela|website=Quién|date=2009-08-04|accessdate=2016-09-23|archive-date=2020-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031165657/https://www.quien.com/sociales/2009/08/04/manuel-garcia-rulfo-galan-de-pelicula|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

